comment: По клику на первый труп убитого Хейнриксом культиста

languages.text: Этот культист погиб не от милосердного и быстрого удара электричества — его лицо искажено болью, словно его пытали.
A mercifully quick electric shock was not what killed this cultist. His face is contorted in pain as if he was tortured.

languages.text: Dieser Kultist ist nicht durch einen gnädig schnellen elektrischen Schlag gestorben. Sein Gesicht ist schmerzverzerrt, als sei er gefoltert worden.
languages.original_text: A mercifully quick electric shock was not what killed this cultist. His face is contorted in pain as if he was tortured.

traits.locale_text: Dieser Kultist ist nicht durch einen gnädig schnellen elektrischen Schlag gestorben. Sein Gesicht ist schmerzverzerrt, als sei er gefoltert worden.

languages.text: Ce pauvre cultiste n'est pas mort d'une simple électrocution : la douleur a déformé son visage comme s'il avait été torturé.
languages.original_text: A mercifully quick electric shock was not what killed this cultist. His face is contorted in pain as if he was tortured.

traits.locale_text: Ce pauvre cultiste n'est pas mort d'une simple électrocution : la douleur a déformé son visage comme s'il avait été torturé.

languages.text: 这个死了的邪教徒并不是在电击中瞬间毙命。他的脸痛苦地扭在一起，看起来像是生前受了不少折磨。
languages.original_text: A mercifully quick electric shock was not what killed this cultist. His face is contorted in pain as if he was tortured.

traits.locale_text: 这个死了的邪教徒并不是在电击中瞬间毙命。他的脸痛苦地扭在一起，看起来像是生前受了不少折磨。

languages.text: この魔女団の信者の死因は、ありがたくも手短に済んだ電気ショックではないようだ。男の顔は、まるで拷問を受けたかのように痛みで歪んでいる。
languages.original_text: A mercifully quick electric shock was not what killed this cultist. His face is contorted in pain as if he was tortured.

traits.locale_text: この魔女団の信者の死因は、ありがたくも手短に済んだ電気ショックではないようだ。男の顔は、まるで拷問を受けたかのように痛みで歪んでいる。

languages.text: Una rápida descarga eléctrica no fue lo que mató a este cultista. Su rostro está retorcido por el dolor, como si le hubieran torturado.
languages.original_text: A mercifully quick electric shock was not what killed this cultist. His face is contorted in pain as if he was tortured.

traits.locale_text: Una rápida descarga eléctrica no fue lo que mató a este cultista. Su rostro está retorcido por el dolor, como si le hubieran torturado.

languages.text: Tarikatçıyı öldüren şey, aniden çarpan merhametli bir elektrik şoku değilmiş. Yüzü öncesinde işkence görmüş gibi çarpılmış.
languages.original_text: A mercifully quick electric shock was not what killed this cultist. His face is contorted in pain as if he was tortured.

traits.locale_text: Tarikatçiyi öldüren şey hızlı ve merhametli bir elektrik şoku değilmiş. Yüzü sanki işkence görüyormuş gibi çarpılmış.
